title: Saudi Arabia : number of internet users 2015 to 2023
yAxis: Number of internet users in millions
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of internet users in millions. In total the number of data points it has is 9.
In general Number of internet users in millions has rose over the Year.
Number of internet users in millions is slightly increasing from 2015 to 2020, and finally roughly constant from 2020 to 2023.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest Number of internet users in millions, of value 35.0 was reached at Year 2023
The lowest Number of internet users in millions, of value 21.54 was reported at Year 2015
